name: segmenting7
description:
This is something of a tangent from my previous work, I've used a lot of CLIP guided GAN animation recently and this one I made the hard way pixel by pixel, 12 frames per second.

I was inspired to try out the Piskel app by mumuthestan and after getting a loop I liked together I ran it through CLIP guided diffusion which produced the watercolor and film grain textures. 

I like this one a lot.
